text:
Catherine Weseluck (born August 21, 1970) also credited as Cathy Weseluck is a Canadian actress, comedian, singer, and voice actress.
She was born in Toronto, Ontario, Canada.
Weseluck often works with Ocean Productions in Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada. She acts the voice for characters in anime series. She is the voice of mothers or little boys. Major roles include Near in "Death Note" and Spike in '.
